title: Meet Panthro
description: Panthro may be the strongest cat on Third Earth, but one of his biggest strengths is that he can fix anything!  And the rest of the Thundercats break enough stuff to really put his skills to the test, but it's nothing a pro like Panthro can't handle.

title: Wheels
description: Kim Kil Whan is worried about his daughter's future and asks Jake for some parental advice.

title: TV Knight 6
description: Batman is forced to go to the department store with Alfred, but runs off to watch TV with Commissioner Gordon.

title: Burglar Alarmed/Shotgun Wedding
description: Burglar Alarmed: A new burglar comes to Townsville and his first robbery is at the house of the Powerpuff Girls?/Shotgun Wedding: The Professor tries to find out what a Lumkins really is.

title: Blukic and Driba Go to Area 51
description: A mysterious Galvan arrives and demands Blukic and Driba to give back a super powerful weapon needed to stop a threat to Earth.

title: Lessons for a Master
description: When Iron Baron forces Wu to retrieve the Dragon Armor, things don't go as planned. In Ninjago, Lloyd can only endure so much as he holds onto hope for the Ninjas' return.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Chaotic Clumping
description: Elliott and Mo accidentally take a teleporter together, and find themselves closer than they've ever been before. Will they decide to mutually part ways?

title: Sarah
description: Darwin le pide a Sarah una foto para poner en la portada del anuario escolar. Pero cuando Sarah trata de ayudar, las cosas se complican un poco.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: The Oct-Father
description: When Princess Morbucks steals Octi, Bubbles' reaction surprises everyone, even her sisters.

title: Monster Talent
description: Daffy takes Gossamer under his wing, while Bugs stars in a TV commercial for Speedy's new frozen pizza.

title: Sugar & Spice & Lightning & Frights
description: When two new kids show up at the daycare Duncan and Leshawna take issue with, not what makes them different, but what makes them similar to the newbies.

title: Carmageddon
description: Duncan is rattled when Chef, tired of having his car destroyed, buys a new one that is completely indestructible.

title: You Can't Handle the Tooth
description: Uncle Grandpa and Mr. Gus must rescue Pizza Steve from the Tooth Fairy.

title: Nexo Creativo
description: Cuando KO queda atrapado dentro de un lugar misterioso, se encuentra con otros héroes de Cartoon Network y todos se unen para escapar.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Teen Titans Roar!
description: The Titans are outraged when their favorite cartoon is rebooted so they come up with a plan to get this new show off the air.

title: Four Color Fallout
description: Axel, Galileo, and Sarge get Minergy-transported by Madcap into the pages of Axel's favorite comic book, the hero of which turns out not to be so cool after all.

title: Fish and Visitors
description: Yosemite Sam moves in with Bugs and Daffy and quickly wears out his welcome.

title: Dance Reynaldo Dance
description: Vic is desperate to win the cash prize for the dance contest in Monte Macabre and is frustrated that his partner Val won't let him call all the shots. Instead he chooses a different partner: Reynaldo. But Vic pushes Reynaldo too hard to execute his artistic vision. Eventually he learns that in order to be a success, you have to be equal partners.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals
description: From Trigon to Terra to Darkseid, Robin counts down the worst of the worst: the greatest villains to ever challenge the Teen Titans!

title: Trapped in the Tower
description: During a fun fireworks show, Unikitty and Master Frown become trapped in the horn of the Unikitty Castle when she catches Master Frown messing with her fireworks. Unikitty takes this as an opportunity to figure out why Master Frown is always such a Cranky McCrabby Face all the time, if only Master Frown would let his emotional guard down! She tries all kinds of tactics, a song, a dance, even a firework with a face drawn on it named "Professor Pow Pow, licensed therapist" Getting nowhere, Unikitty ends up raging out and setting the tower and all the fireworks alight. In desperation to not burn alive, Master Frown tells Unikitty a story about a younger Master Frown who was gifted a special lollipop but after a freak chain of events, was broken right before his eyes. Unikitty cries her eyes out and puts out the fires and then reveals it was her plan all along to get Master Frown to talk about his feelings!

title: The Audition
description: The Bears audition to be the next mascot for their favorite cereal. They get so caught up in the process that their competitiveness gets the best of them.

title: Ancianos de arroyo
description: Craig, Kelsey y JP descubren una fortaleza antigua que les perteneció a los primeros niños del bosque.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Los Jovenes Titanes Rugen
description: Los Titanes se indignan cuando su caricatura favorita es reiniciada, así que idean un plan para sacar al nuevo show del aire.

title: The Final Book
description: The last book of Kelsey's favorite fantasy series goes missing from the library, so Craig decides to help her solve the mystery of who took it.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Intergalactic Games
description: Super Hero High is facing off against Korugar Academy in the Intergalactic Games, but Lena Luthor takes advantage of the gathering of supers to enact her villainous plan.

title: Craig y la mesa de los ninos
description: Llegó el Día de Acción de Gracias de la familia Williams, iasí que es hora de reunir a la Mesa de los chicos! Pero cuando, por accidente, Bernard destruye el postre, Craig usa el poder de la Mesa de los chicos como ayuda para salvar a su hermano de un castigo asegurado.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Back with a Vengeance
description: Ben's feeling cocky with the watch. He's unlocked its secret, and now can become any alien he wants, whenever he wants. That's the good news. The bad news is, after finding one another in the depths of space, Kevin 11 and Vilgax have teamed up and have returned to earth to destroy Ben and get the Omnitrix.

title: For the Love of Narwhal
description: Vambre rejects Darlin' Narwhal Magisword as being unfit for battle, but when Prohyas trains and brings out its full potential, Vambre resorts to improper extremes to get it back.

title: Jailbird and Jailbunny
description: After littering at the Grand Canyon and then refusing to pay the fine, Daffy gets himself and Bugs thrown into jail for contempt of court.  Daffy fears for his life, but Bugs embraces the carefree life of prison.

title: Gyranoid of the Future
description: Apple and Onion struggle to ride Gyranoid of the Future, the craziest roller coaster at the carnival.

title: Lost Playground
description: When Aberdale Elementary's beloved playground equipment is replaced with safe, boring alternatives, Clarence and the gang seek out their old playground equipment in the legendary lost playground yard.

title: Tummy Ache
description: Team Tennyson go on a tour of the new Biggie Box Candy Store, but when Toothache breaks out and kidnaps the owner, Mr. Biggie, it is up to Ben to stop the monstrous dentist and save the candy man and his wondrous candy store.

title: Ben 10,000
description: Ben gets sucked into the future by a grown up Gwen. His mission is to help the now all powerful and adult Ben 10,000 seemingly defeat the future versions of Dr. Animo and Vilgax. However, the real reason Ben has been brought to the future is to teach his adult self some humility and the fact he's lost touch with Max and has forgotten what's really important, family.

title: Players of the Lost Park
description: When Team Tennyson visits Raspberry Park for some R & R, they get more than they bargained for. What they think are innocent games of chance are a revenge plot by Zombozo to steal the Rustbuggy and rob Team Tennyson!

title: Verde de Envidia
description: Cuando las noticias locales entrevistan al tío Andrew sobre la invención de su juguete, un envidioso Galileo organiza una obra de teatro en el parque con la ayuda de Axel y el equipo, isolo para ser interrumpido por un Madcap igualmente envidioso que se roba el centro de atención!

title: #NoDerribenElArbol
description: Jessica Cruz y Pam Isley se unen para evitar que un antiguo árbol sea talado, pero ninguna se da cuenta de quien es el alter ego de la otra ni los extremos a los que llegarán para proteger lo que es importante.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Alan
description: Darwin quiere poner a Alan en la portada del anuario escolar, pero la aparente modestia de Alan se interpone.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: The Evolution of Craig
description: Craig rescues a tadpole and decides to raise him into a level 100 frog!

title: Panic in the Lighthouse
description: When Chaotique breaks into Dr. Light's lab, Mega Man must shut down his frenemy and the lab's defenses before either of them gets destroyed!

title: Efectos en Cuatro Colores
description: Axel, Galileo y Sarge son transportados por Minergy por Madcap a las páginas del cómic favorito de Axel, cuyo héroe resulta no ser tan genial después de todo.

title: Heatwave
description: Apple and Onion try to spread cheer during a city-wide heatwave.

title: Icy Nights
description: Ice Bear rides his custom vacuum into the city. But when a gang of techies steal the vacuum, Ice Bear goes on a rescue mission that takes him through the underground world of the city.

title: Lying Around the House/Bubble Boy
description: Lying Around The House: The girls tell little white lies that turn into a big, bad problem./Bubble Boy: Realizing that the only way to beat the Rowdyruff Boys is to join them, Bubbles takes Boomer's place in this rough-and-tumble band of boys.

title: The AB Bakugan Battle League!
description: With all the mayhem and destruction Haavik is causing, the Awesome Brawlers decide that a bit of Bakugan brawling is the perfect distraction to take their minds off all the trouble. With the help of some friends, they start the Awesome Brawler Bakugan Battle league!/ The Awesome Brawler's Bakugan Battle league rages on. Just as the semifinal round comes to a close, an uninvited guest crashes the party, bringing an alarming end to the battle league.

title: The Gauntlet Part 2
description: As Dr. Light and Suna turn the Robot Masters against each other, Mega Man defeats and unmasks his arch nemeses, Lord Obsidian, who turns out to be Sgt. Night in disguise, and finally learns the identity of Namagem, Mega Man's long lost twin brother!

title: Dos mentiras una verdad
description: Cuando Lloyd desenmascara y revela la identidad de Mystake, el Emperador Garmadon acepta a Harumi como su hija de la oscuridad. Mientras tanto, Wu se aferra a su fe al llevar a sus amigos hacia territorios Oni peligrosos esperando encontrar el nido de la Primogénita.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Tiko's Back?!/Arise, Ultimate Infinity!
description: Tiko's Back?!: In order to make Sabrus a 6 faction fusion Bakugan, Haavik heads into the maze to try to capture a golden Bakugan who has brought "mayhem and destruction" to Earth once before - Tiko!/Arise, Ultimate Infinity!: The Awesome Brawlers manage to thwart Haavik's attempt to fuse Tiko with Sabrus, but Haavik ends up escaping with the golden Bakugan, Pyravian. Now the Awesome Brawlers must track down Haavik before he can form his ultimate 6 faction fusion Bakugan.

title: Drawn to Making it Happen with Sidney Keys
description: Cartoon Network celebrates Black History Month with Sidney Keys III, a 15-year-old rising entrepreneur and the founder and CEO of "Books n Bros," an African American literature book club for male youth ages 7-13 years old. Focused on promoting literacy among young Black boys and introducing them to positive representation in literature, Keys' advocacy is paving the way for change by creating a place for boys to be mentored by their "Big Bros" and connect over a shared love for reading.

title: Throwing Shade Part 1
description: Sgt. Night publicly criticizes Dr. Light's views on human & robot unity during a school assembly, invoking the ire of Fire Man and forcing Silicon City's newly minted hero, Mega Man, to intervene.

title: Broke His Crown
description: When Ice King's magic crown goes haywire, Marceline and Princess Bubblegum resort to extreme measures to help him.

title: Ola de Calor
description: Manzana y Cebollín tratan de esparcir alegría durante una ola de calor en toda la ciudad.

title: Drawn to Community
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating awesome kids who are giving back and making a difference to those around them. CN is recognizing extraordinary girls who are channeling their interests into outreach as they are Drawn to… Community!

title: Grizz Helps
description: When his brothers don't need his help for the day, Grizz leaves the cave to assist anyone he can throughout the city.

title: Haavik's Final Show/Miracle Planet
description: Haavik's Final Show: It's the final stage of Haavik's Bakugan Battle League: Dan and Drago Infinity vs. Haavik and his six-faction fusion Bakugan, Sabrus. Once again, the fate of two worlds, Earth and Vestoria rests in the hands of the Awesome Brawlers!/ Miracle Planet: The epic clash between Drago Infinty and Sabrus rages on. The winner of this clash of titans will decide the fate Earth and Vestroia.

title: The Very Best Candy
description: The gang can't decide which of their candy is the best, so they turn it sentient and have it fight to determine the winner.

title: Destino verde
description: Los Ninjas regresan por fin a casa y se unen para detener al Emperador Garmadon, obligando a Lloyd a tomar una decisión que cambiará por siempre a Ninjago.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Haavik's Challenge/Storm Haavik's Tower
description: Haavik's Challenge: Haavik has crashed the Awesome Brawlers Bakugan League, and challenges the Awesome Brawlers in a battle league of his own!/ Storm Haavik's Tower: In order to keep Earth and Vestroia safe and rescue Drago, the Awesome Brawlers agree to enter Haavik's Bakugan Battle League, and race toward Haavik's tower for the final showdown.
